'''2015年巴基斯坦熱浪'''，是指一系列發生在2015年6月，於[[巴基斯坦|巴基斯坦]]的[[熱浪|熱浪]]災情。受災的主要地區包括有[[信德省|信德省]]、[[旁遮普省|旁遮普省]]南部，以及[[俾路支省|俾路支省]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://time.com/3931394/pakistan-sindh-karachi-heatwave-445-dead/|title=The Death Toll from Pakistan's Heatwave Is Now Nearing 450|accessdate=2015-06-24|archive-date=2018-12-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181226145255/http://time.com/3931394/pakistan-sindh-karachi-heatwave-445-dead/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="BBC"/><ref>{{cite news|title=Pakistan heat wave claims at least 140 lives in Karachi|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2015/06/21/asia/pakistan-heat-wave/|accessdate=22 June 2015|publisher=CNN|date=22 June 2015|archive-date=2018-12-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181226145258/https://edition.cnn.com/2015/06/21/asia/pakistan-heat-wave/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/Heatwave-kills-around-400-people-in-Karachi/articleshow/47778102.cms|title=Heatwave kills around 400 people in Karachi|accessdate=2015-06-24|archive-date=2018-12-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181226145358/https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/Heatwave-kills-around-400-people-in-Karachi/articleshow/47778102.cms|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=TOI/><ref name=times>{{cite news|title=A Heat Wave in Pakistan Has Killed Around 140 People|url=https://time.com/3929729/pakistan-heatwave-karachi-heat-stroke/|accessdate=22 June 2015|publisher=Times|date=22 June 2015|archive-date=2018-12-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181226145254/http://time.com/3929729/pakistan-heatwave-karachi-heat-stroke/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。截至2015年6月24日，已有超過1200人死亡，多數在[[卡拉奇|卡拉奇]]，其他地區也有死者<ref name="pak1200nation"/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://indianexpress.com/article/world/neighbours/heatwave-in-pakistan-kills-over-1200-army-called-in-to-deal-with-situation/|title=Heatwave in Pakistan kills over 1,200, army called in to deal with situation|accessdate=2015-06-24|archive-date=2015-06-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150624160033/http://indianexpress.com/article/world/neighbours/heatwave-in-pakistan-kills-over-1200-army-called-in-to-deal-with-situation/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.samaa.tv/pakistan/24-Jun-2015/karachi-heat-deaths-not-linked-to-power-crisis-asif|title=Karachi heat deaths not linked to power crisis: Opposition Leader in the National Assembly Syed Khursheed Shah|access-date=2015-06-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150627070737/http://www.samaa.tv/pakistan/24-Jun-2015/karachi-heat-deaths-not-linked-to-power-crisis-asif|archive-date=2015-06-27|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/2015/06/pakistan-heatwave-death-toll-soars-750-150624062913997.html|title=Pakistan heatwave death toll edges towards 800|accessdate=2015-06-24|archive-date=2015-06-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150624140141/http://www.aljazeera.com/news/2015/06/pakistan-heatwave-death-toll-soars-750-150624062913997.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="pak770"/<ref name="pak700"/><ref name="tnpk600"/><ref name="BBC">{{cite news|title=Heatwave in Pakistan's Sindh province leaves 120 dead|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-33219890|accessdate=22 June 2015|publisher=BBC|date=22 June 2015|archive-date=2016-04-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160408055521/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-33219890|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

此次熱浪發生在[[伊斯蘭教|伊斯蘭教]]的[[齋戒月|齋戒月]]期間，而[[輸電網路|輸電網路]]在齋月的第一天便已損毀，導致大量死亡<ref name="economictimes" /><ref>{{cite news|title=Heat wave kills more than 120 in Pakistan's Karachi|url=http://uk.reuters.com/article/2015/06/22/uk-pakistan-heatwave-idUKKBN0P20DB20150622|accessdate=22 June 2015|publisher=Reuters|date=22 June 2015|archive-date=2018-12-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181226145320/https://uk.reuters.com/article/uk-pakistan-heatwave/heat-wave-kills-more-than-180-in-pakistans-southern-sindh-idUKKBN0P20DB20150622|dead-url=no}}</ref>。此次熱浪在卡拉奇測得的最高溫，僅次於1979年<ref name="BBC"/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-33236067|title=Pakistan heatwave: Emergency measures as toll nears 700|accessdate=2015-06-24|archive-date=2018-12-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181226145341/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-33236067|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 原因 ==
{{link-en|巴基斯坦環境保護局|Pakistan Environmental Protection Agency}}前局長Asif Shuja稱，熱浪是[[全球變暖|全球暖化]]的一種「症狀」，而過度的[[森林開伐|森林開伐]]、建造{{link-en|巴基斯坦高速公路系統|Motorways of Pakistan|超級高速公路}}所鋪設的大面積[[瀝青|瀝青]]，與過快的{{link-en|巴基斯坦的城市化|Urbanisation in Pakistan|城市化發展}}，都使其更加惡化<ref name="TET">{{cite news|title=Heat wave: Under scorching sun, Pakistan swelters|url=http://tribune.com.pk/story/907232/heat-wave-under-scorching-sun-pakistan-swelters/|date=21 June 2015|work=The Express Tribune|accessdate=22 June 2015|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6ZTkUK6Ev?url=http://tribune.com.pk/story/907232/heat-wave-under-scorching-sun-pakistan-swelters/|archivedate=2015-06-22|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他認為，[[地球|地球]]100年來的{{link-en|溫度記錄|Temperature record|平均溫度}}，已由{{convert|15.5|C|F}}上升至{{convert|16.2|C|F}}，所以「我們在[[夏季|夏季]]與[[冬季|冬季]]，都將經受這樣極端的氣候變化」<ref name="TET"/>。Shuja又稱，由於巴基斯坦缺乏先進的氣象預測技術與人員，所以導致了大量傷亡。

由於正值伊斯蘭教的[[齋戒月|齋戒月]]，在熱浪之下仍有不少[[穆斯林|穆斯林]]堅持在日間不飲水，導致身體[[脫水|脫水]]的機會上升，<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.am730.com.hk/article-270207 |title=齋戒月信徒拒喝水 巴基斯坦熱浪830死 |work=AM730 |date=2015-06-25 |access-date=2015-06-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150626141028/http://www.am730.com.hk/article-270207 |archive-date=2015-06-26 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>而巴基斯坦法律禁止穆斯林在齋戒月期間從日出至日落的時段內於公眾地方飲食，<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.france24.com/en/20150624-pakistan-heat-wave-death-toll-750-karachi |title=Death toll from Pakistan heat wave tops 750 |publisher=France 24 |date=2015-06-24 |quote=Under Pakistani law, it is illegal for Muslims to eat or drink in public during daylight hours in Ramadan. |access-date=2015-06-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150626112536/http://www.france24.com/en/20150624-pakistan-heat-wave-death-toll-750-karachi |archive-date=2015-06-26 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>對於那些日間在戶外的人也造成了難題<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://cn.nytimes.com/world/20150624/c24pakistan/dual/ |title=热浪侵袭巴基斯坦致数百人死亡 |work=纽约时报中文网 |date=2015-06-24 |access-date=2015-06-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190213103650/https://cn.nytimes.com/world/20150624/c24pakistan/dual/ |archive-date=2019-02-13 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。面對高溫天氣，伊斯蘭教[[穆夫提|穆夫提]]Mohammad Naeem發佈[[伊斯蘭教令|教令]]容許穆斯林經醫生判斷認為有需要的話，可以在齋戒月的日間飲食。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.nbcnews.com/news/world/pakistani-muslims-told-they-can-eat-during-ramadan-during-heatwave-n380771 |title=Karachi Heat Wave: Some Muslims Can Eat During Ramadan, Cleric Says |work=NBC News |date=2015-06-24 |accessdate=2015-06-25 |archive-date=2015-06-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150625115459/http://www.nbcnews.com/news/world/pakistani-muslims-told-they-can-eat-during-ramadan-during-heatwave-n380771 |dead-url=no }}</ref>另一位教士Tahir Ashrafi亦呼籲有中暑風險的穆斯林可以不守齋戒。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.abc.net.au/news/2015-06-23/death-toll-from-pakistan-heatwave-rises/6568350 |title=Heatwave kills at least 780 in Karachi, Pakistan during holy month of Ramadan, but rain expected soon |work=ABC News (Australian Broadcasting Corporation) |date=2015-06-24 |accessdate=2015-06-25 |archive-date=2015-06-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150624064702/http://www.abc.net.au/news/2015-06-23/death-toll-from-pakistan-heatwave-rises/6568350 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 災情 ==
