ingtonpost.com/2015/06/23/pakistan-heat-wave_n_7642576.html?ncid=tweetlnkushpmg00000067&ir=India&adsSiteOverride=in&ec_carp=5070109826782515865|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="auto"/>，而信德省的死亡總數是830至1213人之間<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.deccanherald.com/content/485478/heatwave-pakistan-kills-over-1200.html|title=Heatwave in Pakistan kills over 1,200|accessdate=2015-06-24|archive-date=2018-12-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181226145359/https://www.deccanherald.com/content/485478/heatwave-pakistan-kills-over-1200.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dnd.com.pk/over-1200-died-due-to-heatwave-across-sindh-khursheed-shah-tells-na/94492|title=Over 1,200 died due to heatwave across Sindh, Opposition Leader in the National Assembly Syed Khursheed Shah tells NA|accessdate=2015-06-24|archive-date=2018-12-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181226145311/https://dnd.com.pk/over-1200-died-due-to-heatwave-across-sindh-khursheed-shah-tells-na/94492|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dawn.com/news/1190163|title=Sindh heatwave death toll climbs to 830|accessdate=2015-06-24|archive-date=2018-12-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181226145318/https://www.dawn.com/news/1190163|dead-url=no}}</ref>。已知有119具屍體被運至{{link-en|阿巴斯·沙希德醫院|Abbasi Shaheed Hospital}}，279具屍體運往「真納研究生醫療中心」（{{link-en|Jinnah Postgraduate Medical Centre|Jinnah Postgraduate Medical Centre}}，縮寫：JPMC，簡稱真納醫院，Jinnah Hospital），98具屍體運往{{link-en|市民醫院|Civil Hospital}}（Civil Hospital）；而其他遺體也被轉運到各民營醫院<ref name="pak770"/><ref name=TOI/><ref name=economictimes>{{cite news|title=Heatwave in Pakistan's Sindh province leaves 141 dead|url=http://economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/international/world-news/heatwave-in-pakistans-sindh-province-leaves-141-dead/articleshow/47762743.cms|accessdate=22 June 2015|publisher=Economic Times|date=22 June 2015|archive-date=2018-12-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181226145408/https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/internationa