== 氣溫紀錄 ==
此次在巴基斯坦南部測得的高溫<ref>{{cite web|url=http://blogs.tribune.com.pk/story/28240/heatwave-perhaps-sindh-can-take-lessons-from-ahmedabads-heat-action-plan/|title=#HeatWave: Sindh can take lessons from Ahmedabad’s Heat Action Plan|access-date=2015-06-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150626113406/http://blogs.tribune.com.pk/story/28240/heatwave-perhaps-sindh-can-take-lessons-from-ahmedabads-heat-action-plan/|archive-date=2015-06-26|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，有[[拉爾卡納|拉爾卡納]]、錫比（Sibi）的{{convert|49|C}}，卡拉奇為{{convert|45|C}}。在旁遮普省南部的木爾坦有{{convert|40|C}}的記錄；而俾路支省的部分地區也受到影響，如錫比與土爾巴特（Turbat）的{{convert|49|C}}<ref name="TOI"/><ref name="TET"/><ref name="GEO">{{cite news|title=Temperature soars to 46, load shedding adds to woes|url=http://www.geo.tv/article-188612-Temperature-soars-to-46-load-shedding-adds-to-woes|date=20 June 2015|work=Geo TV|accessdate=22 June 2015|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6ZTnVsAHQ?url=http://www.geo.tv/article-188612-Temperature-soars-to-46-load-shedding-adds-to-woes|archivedate=2015-06-22|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="PT">{{cite news|title=Pakistan melts under scorching heat, hottest year recorded|url=http://www.pakistantoday.com.pk/2015/06/21/national/pakistan-melts-under-scorching-heat-hottest-year-recorded/|date=21 June 2015|work=Pakistan Today|accessdate=22 June 2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150626162648/http://www.pakistantoday.com.pk/2015/06/21/national/pakistan-melts-under-scorching-heat-hottest-year-recorded/|archive-date=2015-06-26|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

